text: Kamysh-Uzyak () is a rural locality (a village) in Matrayevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 64 km from Zilair, 13 km from Matrayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kamysh-Uzyak
